          <a href="user?id=gruez" class="hnuser">gruez</a> <span class="age"><a href="item?id=14336378">3 hours ago</a></span> <span id="unv_14336378"></span><span class="par"></span> <a class="togg" n="1" href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="return toggle(event, 14336378)"></a>          <span class='storyon'></span>
                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="c00">because the patented method is better than any non-patented method, and the patent owner agreed to license them to competitors under FRAND.<span>
