                  <span class="c00">The term &quot;standard&quot; in this context means &quot;governed by a standardization body like 3GPP, etc.&quot;  This is significant because the FRAND limitation comes not from legal restrictions on patents but from these standardization bodies themselves.  &quot;Yes, QCOM, you made a far superior air interface for radios.  In recognition of your superior design, we will use your patents as our standard but only if you agree to license it to anyone on &#x27;fair&#x27; terms.&quot;<span>
