                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="c00">LTE is a standard created by a standards body of which Qualcomm is a member. The standards body requires by contract that for things added to the standard that are covered by its members&#x27; patents, those patents are licensed under FRAND terms. This was not done here.<span>
              </span><div class='reply'>        <p><font size="1">
